            <p id= "infoFont">A quick peek behind the Arts & Entertainment desk reveals a clutter of CDs, DVDs, books and various press copies sent to us by generous promoters. Most of it, unfortunately, has never gone on to receive attention by our staff â€“ until now. Stuff from the Shelf is a feature that explores the stacks of forgotten media, hoping to find a rare gem in the rough.</p>
            <i> Webpage - Aalhad Patankar, Reviews- Daily Bruin A&E </i>
